
# ⏰ Neon Digital Clock

A modern and responsive Digital Clock built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It displays the current time, date, day, AM/PM, and a dynamic greeting with a modern cyberpunk-inspired UI.

---

## ✨ Features

- ⏰ Live Digital Clock
- 📅 Current Date
- 📆 Current Day
- 🌞 AM / PM Indicator
- 👋 Dynamic Greeting
- 💜 Neon Cyberpunk UI
- 📱 Responsive Design
- ⚡ Real-Time Updates Every Second

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

---

